        <entry>
          <string>Description</string>
          <string>OPCODES:
1: AND
2: NAND
3: OR
4: NOR
5: XOR
6: XNOR
7: NOT
8: ADD
9: SUB
10: MUL
11: DIV
12: SHIFT (A shifted by B)
13: is A == to B
14: NEGITIVE
15: BIT COUNT
16: Bit selector
Inputs:
A: input 1
B: input 2
Outputs: 
Over: Overflow/remainder
O: output from operation</string>
        </entry>
